Are you spending money on AI apps for the “Barbie box trend”? Well I did mine completely FREE using ChatGPT (no paid version needed)

SAVE THIS POST! 

I got 4 different doll-like images that actually looked like me.(some what) 🤡

Here’s how you can create your personalized doll image (for FREE):

	1.	Download the ChatGPT app (or use it on desktop)—no Pro version needed.
	2.	Upload one close-up front facing picture and one full-length photo of yourself (good lighting, clean background).
	3.	Use this exact prompt (customize for your style):

“I have a heart-shaped face and long hair with brown highlights styled in outward curls. I’m a beauty content creator and I love coffee. I want to look like a collectible doll in retail style. Add my name, ‘[Your Name]’ in the title. Style me in a confident, fuller-figured Barbie aesthetic. Place me inside a box or retail setup. Add beauty elements like eyeshadow palettes or makeup products, one in my hand and the rest beside me. Make it clean and aesthetic with soft lighting.”

	4.	ChatGPT lets you generate up to 4 images for free—but after that, you’ll need to wait 12 hours before you can try again.
	5.	If you prompt well, you’ll get exactly what you want, and maybe even 4 different styles!
	•	but if the generated image doesn’t suit your taste you can ask ChatGPT to change or enhance it atleast thrice to adjust your look or the background, props, or even clothing for more uniqueness 

Thank me later 💕
